---
const SITE_URL = import.meta.env.SITE_URL || import.meta.env.PUBLIC_SITE_URL || 'https://www.inghengcredit.com';
---
<html lang="ms">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Peta Laman - Ing Heng Credit</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Peta laman HTML untuk Ing Heng Credit Malaysia - Pembiayaan peralatan, pinjaman perniagaan, dan pembiayaan SME." />
    <meta name="robots" content="index,follow" />
    <link rel="canonical" href={`${SITE_URL}/sitemap/ms.html`} />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <header>
        <h1>Peta Laman</h1>
        <p>Laman ini menyediakan pandangan yang mudah dibaca untuk semua laman di laman web Ing Heng Credit. Untuk enjin carian, sila gunakan <a href={`${SITE_URL}/sitemap-index.xml`}>peta laman XML</a> kami.</p>
      </header>

      <section class="important-pages">
        <h2>Laman Penting</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/ms/" priority="1.0">Laman Utama</a></li>
          <li><a href="/ms/about" priority="0.9">Tentang Kami</a></li>
          <li><a href="/ms/contact" priority="0.9">Hubungi</a></li>
          <li><a href="/ms/equipment" priority="0.9">Pembiayaan Peralatan</a></li>
          <li><a href="/ms/services" priority="0.9">Perkhidmatan</a></li>
          <li><a href="/ms/calculator" priority="0.9">Kalkulator Pinjaman</a></li>
          <li><a href="/ms/faq" priority="0.8">Soalan Lazim</a></li>
          <li><a href="/ms/blog" priority="0.8">Blog</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="equipment-pages">
        <h2>Laman Peralatan</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/ms/equipment/bulldozer">Pembiayaan Buldozer</a></li>
          <li><a href="/ms/equipment/crane">Pembiayaan Kren</a></li>
          <li><a href="/ms/equipment/excavator">Pembiayaan Jentolak</a></li>
          <li><a href="/ms/equipment/forklift">Pembiayaan Forklift</a></li>
          <li><a href="/ms/equipment/lorry">Pembiayaan Lori</a></li>
          <li><a href="/ms/equipment/prime-mover">Pembiayaan Prime Mover</a></li>
          <li><a href="/ms/equipment/refrigerated-truck">Pembiayaan Lori Sejuk</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="service-pages">
        <h2>Laman Perkhidmatan</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/ms/services/hire-purchase">Sewa Beli</a></li>
          <li><a href="/ms/services/loan-financing">Pembiayaan Pinjaman</a></li>
          <li><a href="/ms/services/insurance">Insurans</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="resources">
        <h2>Sumber</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href={`${SITE_URL}/sitemap-index.xml`}>Indeks Peta Laman XML</a></li>
          <li><a href={`${SITE_URL}/robots.txt`}>robots.txt</a></li>
          <li><a href="/ms/calculator">Kalkulator Pinjaman</a></li>
          <li><a href="/ms/faq">Soalan Lazim</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <footer>
        <p>Dikemaskinikan: <time>{new Date().toISOString()}</time></p>
        <p>Jumlah laman: <strong>20+</strong></p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>

<style is:inline>
  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
  }
  header {
    border-bottom: 2px solid #b45309;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  h1, h2 {
    color: #b45309;
    margin: 0;
  }
  header p {
    color: #666;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
  }
  header a {
    color: #b45309;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: #f5f5f5;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  a {
    color: #b45309;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
    padding: 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: background-color 0.2s;
  }
  a:hover {
    background-color: #f0f0f0;
  }
  .priority {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #999;
    margin-left: 0.5rem;
  }
  footer {
    border-top: 2px solid #b45309;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    color: #666;
    text-align: center;
  }
  time {
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
